<h2 class="bold font-l">Walter</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Picture a hideous, blue skinned, demonic cross between Santa and Krampus who is constantly drooling blood that is implied to be toxic. He also swallows people whole and regurgitates them as lumps of coal. </p>
</div>
</div>
